But you dare to meet women secretly in the middle of the night,

290
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:48,680
and two at a time.

291
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,680
If I said

292
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:54,000
one of them came to me for something

293
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,720
and the other came for porridge,

294
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,040
would you believe it?

295
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:07,160
Wait.

296
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,640
What's wrong now?

297
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:10,880
What if we alert the enemy,

298
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:12,360
and it's not what we think,

299
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,680
wouldn't that be awkward?

300
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:14,440
Right.

301
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:15,440
What if that woman

302
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,640
is not a female thief,

303
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:18,280
but has that kind of relationship with him.

304
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:19,600
If we swagger in like this,

305
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,960
wouldn't we ruin their good time?

306
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,160
Makes sense.

307
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,720
Keep it down.

308
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,760
You lecher.

309
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,000
If my sister finds out,

310
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,120
let's see how she deals with you.

311
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,440
Anyway, whether you believe it or not,

312
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,770
it's not what you think.

313
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:49,440
Chu Xiao'er.

314
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:51,720
As a Demon Refiner from Beijing,

315
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:54,120
what is your scheme in coming to our Daqian?

316
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:54,840
And you.

317
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,160
You are no longer Mo Xiaolan now.

318
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,440
Don't just casually

319
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,900
move into a man's mansion.

320
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:00,720
Lady,

321
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,920
does what I do here have anything to do with you?

322
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:05,640
Have you caught the monster harming people in the capital?

323
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,080
You...

324
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,600
Sister Wuhui.

325
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,320
Getting into my young master's bed

326
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,080
and pulling off his blanket,

327
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:11,480
isn't it inappropriate?

328
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,440
What?

329
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,760
Did your young lady agree

330
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:15,620
to share my young master with you?

331
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:23,280
A fallen princess and monster refiner of Beijing,

332
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:25,780
and an unwanted newborn wood demon maid.

333
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:28,520
To think you two are actually huddling together for warmth.

334
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:29,560
This capital

335
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:32,020
is getting harder and harder to understand.

336
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:34,600
You guys chat.

337
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,480
I'm leaving.

338
00:15:35,760 --> 00:15:36,320
Lin Mo,

339
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:37,000
come back.

340
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,920
Give that to me.

341
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:38,520
This has nothing to do with me anymore.

342
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,040
Don't even think about it.

343
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:39,920
Young Master, don't go.

344
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:41,160
She's bullying me.

345
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:41,960
Let him go.

346
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,720
Keep your hands to yourself.

347
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,400
No magic allowed.

348
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:48,560
I'm not afraid of a fistfight.

